tool_description: International Bridge Blue API allows developers to integrate shipping labels and fulfillment within their e-commerce businesses and online marketplaces. The API offers price comparison, label printing, manifest generation, transactions details and tracking features.
name: International Bridge Blue
title: International Bridge Blue

--------- | ------- | -----------

import requests

url = "https://international-bridge-blue.p.rapidapi.com/v1/manifests/manifest_number"

            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "international-bridge-blue.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

print(response.json())
